Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.53,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方虽然漂亮 但是对家里蹲来说太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.54,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 「乳头」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.54,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(452.5,454)\fs21\3c&H00FFFF&}chi{\r\fs21}kubi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.64,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.74,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,「比基尼」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.74,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,454)\fs21\3c&H00FFFF&}bi{\r\fs21}kini
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.81,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔 你什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.87,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,换上比基尼之前 应该把衣服给去掉才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.00,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:19.18,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,真是十分抱歉 没有体会到您的意图…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:20.27,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.97,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑 给我认真…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.10,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.21,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那么「行李」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.21,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(450,454)\fs21\3c&H00FFFF&}ni{\r\fs21}motsu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.03,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.79,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就「旋风」如何？
