Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:31.73,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.63,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,结果万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有比基尼 没穿小裤裤的史蒂芙就变成18禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从裙底看比基尼 也别有一番风味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不胜惶恐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.27,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:45.97,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,「女装」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:45.97,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,454)\fs21\3c&H00FFFF&}j{\r\fs21}oseihuku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹啊 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三点不露 但是鞋子袜子都还在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连狗狗项圈也还在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 这比全裸更赞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这明显是全年龄 确实健全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适度色情但却不下流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把这里称为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「超健全空间」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 简直GJ
