Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.80,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.32,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 但总会觉得困吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.18,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳都快升起了 你还是投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.26,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,「外核」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.26,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,454)\fs21\3c&H00FFFF&}ga{\r\fs21}ikaku
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:49.81,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您觉得累了 可以故意输掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:53.52,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,对于脆弱的「人类种」来说 已经让我很享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:53.52,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.5,454)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:54.43,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,「时钟」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:54.43,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,454)\fs21\3c&H00FFFF&}ku{\r\fs21}rokku
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:59.64,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,老是把无力和脆弱挂在嘴边 真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.80,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,「创造物」
